{
  "title": "ISic003505. Inscription recording architect of the Bouleuterion",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Andoni Llamazares; edition source: <a href=\"http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/3PK3JKXR\">http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/3PK3JKXR</a></div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἄσκλαπος Διοδώρου Ταυρέας\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἄσκλαπος\">Ἄσκλαπος</span>  <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Διοδώρου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Διοδώρου\">Διοδώρου</span></span>  <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"secondName\" data-text=\"Ταυρέας\">Ταυρέας</span></span>  <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-text=\"ἐπιστάτας\">ἐπιστάτας</span>  <br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Βίβακος Τιττέλου Ποσθαῖος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Βίβακος\">Βίβακος</span>  <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Τιττέλου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Τιττέλου\">Τιττέλου</span></span>  <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"secondName\" data-text=\"Ποσθαῖος\">Ποσθαῖος</span></span>  <br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span><span data-text=\"ἀρχιτεκτόνησε\">ἀρχιτεκτόνησε</span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Andoni Llamazares; edition source: <a href=\"http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/3PK3JKXR\">http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/3PK3JKXR</a></div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Ἄσκλαπος Διοδώρου Ταυρέας\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἄσκλαπος\">ΑΣΚΛΑΠΟΣ</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Διοδώρου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Διοδώρου\">ΔΙΟΔΩΡΟΥ</span></span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"secondName\" data-text=\"Ταυρέας\">ΤΑΥΡΕΑΣ</span></span><br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-text=\"ἐπιστάτας\">ΕΠΙΣΤΑΤΑΣ</span><br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Βίβακος Τιττέλου Ποσθαῖος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Βίβακος\">ΒΙΒΑΚΟΣ</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Τιττέλου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Τιττέλου\">ΤΙΤΤΕΛΟΥ</span></span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"secondName\" data-text=\"Ποσθαῖος\">ΠΟΣΘΑΙΟΣ</span></span><br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span><span data-text=\"ἀρχιτεκτόνησε\">ΑΡΧΙΤΕΚΤΟΝΗΣΕ</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span><span>text according to Ampolo and Erdas 2019</span></span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag</a></p>  <p>Asklapos Taureas, son of Diodorus, was the overseer. Bibakos Posthaios, son of Tittelos, was the architect.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 50.1020 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a></li><li> Gualtherus 1624 [1625] 323 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001931\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001931</a></li><li> Franz 1853 5547 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001250\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001250</a></li><li> Kaibel 1890 <a href=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\" target=\"_blank\">292</a>  <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072</a></li><li> Hoffmann 1904 5193 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000817\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000817</a></li><li> Nenci 2000 810-811 tav.156 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001726\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001726</a></li><li> De Vido 2003 400 no.13 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002041\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002041</a></li><li> Dubois 2008 88 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000160\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000160</a></li><li> Ampolo and Erdas 2019 G14 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001036\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001036</a></li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"><p>Large, thinly carved letters of wide module. Alpha with broken bar; epsilon with equal width horizontal strokes; kappa with short arms; theta and omicron full size; theta with detached cross-bar; pi with overlapping cross-bar; sigma with horizontal outer strokes, shallow inner strokes; omicron rhomboid and closed.</p> Line 1-4  84-98  Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
